
NEB code 1.5

The Nudged-Elastic-Band method is realized in 'imd_neb.c'. It is parallized with MPI. Each image will be handled by one CPU.
It is developed with IMD version Nov 2007 and the codes are provided here.
The imd_neb module should compatible with the later versions, please check the IMD mainpage.

Realized features:
basic NEB
improved tangent estimation
free end method
automatic k adjustment
angle check (*.eng file)
coordinate distance (spring length, *.eng file)
multi climbing image method
multi sliding image method
smart climb & slide method


